---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<section id="services">
  <div
    class="mx-auto w-full lg:px-24 max-w-7xl md:px-12 items-center px-8 py-24 scroll-mt-12"
  >
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-xl text-center">
      <div>
        <h3
          class="text-4xl tracking-tight font-medium text-black md:text-5xl font-display"
        >
        Services
      </h3>
     </div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl pt-12">
        <h2 class="sr-only">Features.</h2><div>
          <div
            class="grid gap-12 grid-cols-1 lg:space-y-0 lg:text-center md:grid-cols-3"
          >
            <div>
              <div>
                <div
                  class="items-center justify-center text-accent-500 rounded-xl flex h-20 w-20 lg:mr-auto"
                >
                <Image width="100" height="100" src="/House" alt="house" />
                </div><p
                  class="mt-4 text-lg font-semibold leading-6 text-black font-display tracking-tight text-left"
                >
                Residential cleaning
              </div><div class="mt-4 text-gray-500 text-sm leading-loose text-left">
                Residential cleaning provides professional cleaning solutions for homes. Whether you need regular cleaning or a one-time deep cleaning, these services can be tailored to fit your specific needs. Personalization is allowed which helps you focus on specific areas of your home such as bedrooms, living spaces, kitchens, or bathrooms. You can choose from various packages, including weekly, bi-weekly, or monthly cleaning cadence. 
              </div>
            </div><div>
              <div>
                <div
                  class="items-center justify-center text-accent-500 bg-gray-100 rounded-xl flex h-10 w-10 lg:mx-auto"
                >
                  <ion-icon
                    aria-label="scan outline"
                    class="hydrated md h-4 w-4"
                    name="scan-outline"
                    role="img"></ion-icon>
                </div><p
                  class="mt-4 text-lg font-semibold leading-6 text-black font-display tracking-tight text-left"
                >
                Apartment Cleaning
                </p>
              </div><div class="mt-4 text-gray-500 text-sm text-left">
                Apartment cleaning provides professional cleaning solutions for apartments and condos. This service will ensure that your living area continues to be tidy, orderly and comfortable whether youâ€™re a busy professional, family or student. Personalization is allowed which helps you focus on specific areas of your home such as bedrooms, living spaces, kitchens, or bathrooms. You can choose from various packages, including weekly, bi-weekly, or monthly cleaning cadence. 
              </div>
            </div><div>
              <div>
                <div
                  class="items-center justify-center text-accent-500 bg-gray-100 rounded-xl flex h-10 w-10 lg:mx-auto"
                >
                  <ion-icon
                    aria-label="scan outline"
                    class="hydrated md h-4 w-4"
                    name="scan-outline"
                    role="img"></ion-icon>
                </div><p
                  class="mt-4 text-lg font-semibold leading-6 text-black font-display tracking-tight text-left"
                >
                Move In & Out Cleaning
                </p>
              </div><div class="mt-4 text-gray-500 text-sm text-left">
                The primary purpose of this service is to prepare the space for the next occupant. This service includes a deep cleaning service and the disinfecting of key areas such as kitchens, bedrooms, living spaces, bathrooms and basements. Hiring professional move-in and out cleaners saves you time and allows you ensure that there is a successful transition during your moving process. 
              </div>
            </div>
            </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
